<item>
            <title>[RAVE-829] When returning from Admin Interface, user is always redirected to &quot;Main&quot; workspace</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/RAVE-829</link>
                <project id="12311290" key="RAVE">Rave</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The last used workspace is not recalled when a user returns from the admin interface. Instead, always the main workspace is opened.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12612388">RAVE-829</key>
            <summary>When returning from Admin Interface, user is always redirected to &quot;Main&quot; workspace</summary>
